desc: Cortel Designs makes the best through the lens loupes for surgeons, eyeglass loupes for dentists, and custom surgical loupes for designer glasses: Ray Ban, Oakley, Coach, Bolle, Michael Kors. We also carry battery powered surgical headlights, LED surgeon headlamps, and loupe cases to keep your eyewear clean and safe.

layout.text: Our loupes are custom built for you!
